message: Prioritize using 'vial' on solid ingredients, as this consistently creates valuable liquid extracts (value 30). Avoid using 'vial' on gas ingredients, as this leads to botched extractions and negative values. Be very cautious with the 'filter' tool; in this run, it consistently reduced item value. The highest scores were achieved by combining exactly two liquid extracts: specifically, combining a magical liquid extract with a mundane liquid extract often yielded 70-80 value. Combining two magical or two mundane liquid extracts yielded 60. Combining three or more items, especially if any were 'botched' or 'poorly-filtered', or combining liquids with gases, drastically reduced the value, often to 0 or negative. Stick to simple, two-liquid combinations for best results.

message: Focus on extracting one magical solid (e.g., unicorn horn, mandrake root) and one mundane solid (e.g., dandelion, frog leg) using the 'vial' to get two 30-value liquid extracts. Then, combine these two extracts (one magical, one mundane) to often immediately get a 100-value item. If you have initial magical liquids, try combining them directly with mundane liquid extracts. Filtering is most effective on combined, complex liquids, sometimes turning negative or moderate values into high ones, but often degrades single extracts.

Use 'filter' on a natural magical liquid (like kraken ink or basilisk venom) to get a 'filtered magical liquid'. 3. Combine these two items for 100 points. Avoid filtering extracted liquids directly, as it often results in 'botched filtering' and lower value. Combining liquids with gases initially results in negative values, but filtering that combined item can yield 80 points.

message: Focus on creating extracts. Use 'vial' on solid ingredients: 'magical solid' + 'vial' -> 'magical liquid extract' (value 30) and 'mundane solid' + 'vial' -> 'mundane liquid extract' (value 30). Combining a 'magical liquid extract' with a 'mundane liquid extract' consistently creates a 100-value item. 'Filter' also works on liquids to get value 30 items if no solids are available for extraction, and these can also be combined with magical extracts.
